result.adr_address: 142 Tung Lo Wan Rd, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 142 Tung Lo Wan Rd, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Sushi Hana

reviews.text:
Great service and all dishes are well prepared. The staff are friendly and the environment is comfortable and spacious. 

 I ordered the 12 piece sushi lunch set and found every piece awesome. I do think that each piece was slightly over seasoned but other than that I would definitely recommend this place.
Had lunch there with my parents. Very nice sushi and good prices for lunch set. Around 300 for the sushi set. The restaurant is sparkling clean and not so busy. We enjoyed it much.

I came here for lunch and ordered the twelve piece sushi set. There is a couple of choices for lunch sets and the price will range between 380-500 hkd. Except for the omakase which is 800 hkd. Each lunch set comes with a crab steamed egg, miso soup, and dessert or coffee in addition to your main course. 

Food: 4.25 stars
Service: 4.5 stars
Environment: 4 stars
Value: 3.75 stars
Overall: 4.25 stars

The sushi set I ordered were all different types of seafood and spanned a wide variety of different types of seafood and fish. I was served scallop, shrimp, squid in addition to toro, amberjack and other types of fish. The fish quality is very good and each piece was individually served a nice pace as opposed to being served all at once.  I definitely would like to come back to try the omakase the next time I’m here.
Awesome Omakase. High quality food. Nice friendly service. Tina of fresh choices and good pieces
Super value for money for lunch.
